reviewText: decent collection of movies. not perfect but defintely good for my daughter
nice collection, I love Christmas movies.
Good selection of Christmas season shows

I absolutely love Christmas so I am always looking for Christmas movies to watch with my family. These cartoon movies are so adorable and there are  different movies so you can have plenty of family time this Christmas. I received the dvd within just  few days and it works great. This is a must have.
